# Gaps controls
bindsym $mod+Shift+plus gaps outer all plus 5
bindsym $mod+Shift+minus gaps outer all minus 5
bindsym $mod+Shift+w gaps outer all set 0
bindsym $mod+Shift+KP_Add gaps inner all plus 5
bindsym $mod+Shift+KP_Subtract gaps inner all minus 5

## System Commands
bindsym $mod+Shift+c reload
bindsym $mod+Shift+r restart
